---
title: Quick Moroccan-Style Pork & Veggies with Currant Couscous & Yoghurt
description: Couscous – the grain so nice they named it twice! Here we’ve added sweet currants for a pop of flavour and topped the whole
thing off with a mildly spiced pork mince and greens. And don’t forget the dollop of yoghurt – the creamy and cooling addition
that brings this nutritious meal together.

 *This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
